<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的老家，<delay20 />
在<delay8 />偏远的<delay8 />乡下。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说来<tag a="110" b="0" />之前有个朋友说着，
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />“我不想待在这种乡下地方！<delay8 />我要当演员！”<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后<delay20 />离开了老家。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然最近渐渐有点名气了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但她最适合的角色，<delay8 />还是乡下女孩儿。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道，<delay20 />那家伙这样就满足了吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我的老家，<delay8 />那儿的人都很热情，
是个很好的地方哦！！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但就是<delay8 />地大人少，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在家附近转悠的时候，<delay8 />
很少碰得到其他人呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而在<tag a="110" b="33" />的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很容易遇到朋友，这点很好！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的老家在<delay8 />很偏远的乡下，
物质生活很匮乏。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />住在那儿还是挺开心的！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和朋友逃学，一起聊些幼稚的话题，<delay20 />
或在空地上放烟花。<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算总是被<delay8 />那附近的老奶奶数落，<delay8 />
也都是很开心的回忆呢！<delay40 />
<size value="75" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那个老奶奶真的好可怕啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<size value="100" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="010_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />上次因为我的大意，<delay8 />忘记浇水，<delay20 />
我的宝贝花儿就那么枯萎了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那花可是生日的时候，<delay8 />朋友送我的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真的<delay8 />很自责<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为什么我没能<delay8 />
照顾好它们。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />仔细一看<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />枯萎的花朵里<delay20 />竟然留有种子！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我用<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我<tag a="110" b="10" />的名誉起誓！<delay20 />
这次<delay8 />一定会好好照顾它们的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不久前，<delay8 />我的宝贝花儿枯萎了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明明前一天<delay8 />花还开得好好的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好在<delay8 />我查阅了各种资料，
浇了水、<delay8 />修剪了残枝败叶和枯萎的花，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最后终于<delay8 />重新开出了花！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你养的花也枯萎了，<delay20 />
千万别马上放弃，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要把所有可能挽救的方法<delay8 />都试一试哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前不久，<delay8 />就因为我的懈怠，<delay20 />
养的宝贝花儿枯萎了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当时我的脑袋里<delay8 />真的是一片空白。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />我没有放弃，还是继续照顾它们。<delay20 />
渐渐地，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它们又有了生气！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的！<delay8 />那时候<delay20 />我见识到了，<delay8 />
花儿们<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />顽强的生命力！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很庆幸<delay8 />自己没有放弃！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="15 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我总是<delay8 />控制不住<delay8 />
要熬夜呢！</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="021_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总想着<delay8 />今天要早点睡！<delay20 />
在睡前<delay8 />打算看一小会儿漫画，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果一看起来啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总是很好奇<delay8 />接下来的剧情，<delay8 />
于是就停不下来了。<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最后<delay8 />就变成了<delay8 />
“干脆看完这一本吧！”<delay20 />这样的想法。<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" />转眼<delay8 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就到早上了。</message>
	<message label="021_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次想着<delay8 />今天一定要早睡的时候，<delay20 />
总会接到<delay8 />朋友的电话。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要问<delay20 />是什么事<tag a="110" b="0" />？
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那当然<delay8 />是朋友来找我倾诉他们的烦恼了。<delay40 />
<size value="75" />虽然有时候也只是闲聊而已<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><size value="100" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当然了！<delay8 />
再晚睡<delay8 />我早上也能起得来！<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />靠的是意志力！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大晚上的，<delay8 />
我就戴着耳机听喜欢的乐队的歌。<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果<delay8 />渐渐地嗨起来了，<pageBreak />等我回过神来，<delay8 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />已经嗨得像在看现场表演一样，<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还会喊着“哇哦！！”<delay8 />之类的。<pageBreak />听完后<delay8 />也一直平静不下来，
完全睡不着！<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />这样好像有点扰民呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="1f 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近我收到了，<delay8 />
从老家寄来的特产水果。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />本来以为<delay8 />我肯定已经吃腻了。<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但打开箱子的瞬间，<delay8 />闻到那个熟悉的香味，<delay20 />
就感觉鼻头一酸呢！</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="031_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次我也要寄一些<delay8 />这里特产的<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />回去！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要是也有重要的人，<delay8 />
也可以给他们寄一些！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 />眼泪马上就收住了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想起以前<delay8 />叛逆的时候<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />好想忘掉！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一个能够回去的地方，<delay20 />
是给内心的<delay8 />一个支撑。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因它我们能更安心地生活。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040" attrib="29 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你别看我<delay8 />这样，<delay8 />
我可是很喜欢照顾小孩儿的！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以，<delay8 />我也经常照看附近的孩子呢！</message>
	<message label="041" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="041_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看着他们那么小，<delay8 />
每天还在努力生活着，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会觉得<delay8 />自己也要加油才行！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然能让我觉得要更加打起精神来，<delay20 />
他们很了不起啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="041_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然总是为他们忙得团团转，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />只要看到那开心的笑脸，<delay8 />
就会被他们的可爱所打败！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />不过，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要让一个孩子坐在肩头一小时，<delay20 />
真的超级累<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="041_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />小孩子长大<delay8 />是很快的，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />渐渐就变得能说会道的。<delay20 />
在身边看着他们的变化，真的很有意思！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />也不知道是不是他们变得害羞了，<delay20 />
都不来向我撒娇了！<delay8 />
感觉有点寂寞啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="050" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="050_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我非常喜欢<delay8 />种植花卉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当亲手种下的种子开出花朵的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都会开心得<delay8 />想要手舞足蹈。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 />大家好像都对我喜欢花这事感到意外。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我老家的朋友<delay20 />还跟我说，
<delay20 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起可爱的花朵，食虫类植物更适合我。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="32" />上的大家是不是也这样认为呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />对了！<delay frames="40" />我喜欢花这事儿，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你帮我去告诉大家吧！</message>
	<message label="050_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿！<delay20 />你听我说啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是之前<delay20 />我回老家的时候听说的。<delay20 />
老家的朋友之间<delay8 />流传着一个奇怪的传言。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说我搬来这座<tag a="110" b="32" />住，<delay20 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是为了<delay8 />和无人岛的巨大生物对决……<delay20 />
也不知道是谁这样乱传的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我自己听了都忍不住笑了出来！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得<delay20 />老家的朋友，<delay8 />
是不是<delay8 />把我当成那个超级什么什么了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="060" attrib="3d 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />挑选礼物，<delay20 />
可真是件难事啊！</message>
	<message label="061" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="061_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对我来说，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要是对方想着我，
为我用心挑选的礼物，<delay8 />我都很喜欢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />原来如此！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这才是<delay8 />最重要的啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="061_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要送符合对方爱好的东西，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但又感觉<delay8 />对方应该已经拥有了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想和对方商量一下再决定，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是这样就没有惊喜了～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是让人烦恼。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="061_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底应该送什么样的礼物，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能让对方感受到我炙热的友情？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />炙热<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用超级辣的<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" /><delay20 />来表达
我的情感有多炙热，你觉得如何？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>